#. lang="pi"><section class="sutta" id="thig1.2"><article><div
#. class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "thig1.2:1.1"
msgid "Therīgāthā"
msgstr "Verses of the Senior Nuns"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thig1.2:2.1"
msgid "Ekakanipāta"
msgstr "The Book of the Ones"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig1.2:3.1"
msgid "2. Muttātherīgāthā"
msgstr "1.2. Muttā"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc2"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts2"></a>
msgctxt "thig1.2:4.1"
msgid "“Mutte muccassu yogehi,"
msgstr "Muttā, be released from your bonds,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig1.2:4.2"
msgid "cando rāhuggahā iva;"
msgstr "like the moon released from Rāhu’s grip."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig1.2:4.3"
msgid "Vippamuttena cittena,"
msgstr "When your mind is released,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig1.2:4.4"
msgid "anaṇā bhuñja piṇḍakan”ti."
msgstr "enjoy your alms free of debt."

#. </p></blockquote><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a>
msgctxt "thig1.2:5.1"
msgid ""
"Itthaṃ sudaṃ bhagavā muttaṃ sikkhamānaṃ imāya gāthāya abhiṇhaṃ ovadatīti."
msgstr ""
"It was thus that the Buddha regularly advised the trainee nun Muttā with "
"these verses."
